 Features
1.Real-time face detection using Haar Cascade
2.Capture and save cropped face images with a single key press
3.Automatically stores images in a specified folder
4.Lightweight and easy to run on any system with a webcam

 Technologies Used
1.Python
2.OpenCV
3.Haar Cascade Classifier

 How to Use
1.Clone this repository
2.Run the script:
python face_image_collector.py
3.Press c to capture and save detected faces
4.Press q to quit the application
